tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE PatientData (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(50),
    admission_date TIMESTAMP,
    discharge_date TIMESTAMP,
    age INT,
    diagnosis_code INT
)

CREATE TABLE patient_data (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  admission_date DATE,
  discharge_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE admission_records (
  record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  admission_date DATE,
  discharge_date DATE,
  diagnosis VARCHAR(255),
  treatment VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE resource_allocation (
  allocation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  record_id INT,
  resource_type VARCHAR(50),
  quantity INT,
  cost DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE patient_data (patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
patient_name VARCHAR(50),
admission_date DATE,
admission_reason TEXT,
admission_rate FLOAT);

CREATE TABLE resource_allocation (resource_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
resource_name VARCHAR(50),
resource_type VARCHAR(50),
quantity INT);

CREATE TABLE algorithm_parameters (algorithm_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
algorithm_name VARCHAR(50),
training_data_table VARCHAR(50),
forecasted_rates_table VARCHAR(50),
accuracy FLOAT);

CREATE TABLE training_data (data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
patient_id INT,
admission_date DATE,
resource_id INT,
resource_quantity INT);

CREATE TABLE forecasted_rates (forecast_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
patient_id INT,
forecast_date DATE,
forecasted_rate FLOAT);
